# The root .eslintrc.json is the legacy Next/Airbnb config for the old Supabase
# app being migrated. Keep it from linting the v2 monorepo (apps/* + packages/*):
# it applies Next-only rules to backend code, and its plugin:prettier/recommended
# fires prettier/prettier errors at a width that conflicts with .prettierrc.json
# (120) — un-fixable on save, since prettier-on-save already considers them clean.
#
# v2 has its own flat config (@avkash/eslint-config, typescript-eslint, no prettier
# rule); wiring it per-package is a follow-up. Until then v2 relies on prettier +
# tsc for formatting/type-safety, and this legacy linter stays out of its way.
apps/
packages/

# Build artifacts / vendored
**/.next
**/.turbo
**/dist
node_modules
